Video footage of a woman being knocked over by a hospital bus in the UK has gone viral. The CCTV footage shows two women walking in Lancashire, in northwest England, when a hospital bus zooms into a pick-up area, knocking one woman down. Despite being flung to the ground, the woman gets up and brushes herself off. The Metro reports that officials have said they are "appalled" after seeing the footage, explaining that pedestrians should feel safe.